title: A Backdoor by Me :)

embed.description: Game saving Udyr Jungle backdoor by Musterpulse of the OCE Server.

body:
I'm not usually one to self advertise or anything, In fact, I'm not really. But anyways I decided to upload a clip to share with the world, by me, from a recent game I played as Udryer the Sprite Man.

And yes this is the game I was held up with for so long Sart and Tomat0.
I ended it for RG :)
Who knows maybe I will upload more in game adventures in future now that I found a reliable replay system that works ^_^
